    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为预热教程，简短的试玩版内容将帮助你做好迎接完整版游戏中天马行空的冒险的准备。在试玩版中，你将学习制作千奇百怪的美食、缩小鼻涕虫并通过投掷魔法手提箱来使用各种技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到不可思议的避难所</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/217033f7c77149e8fe59a79c87fbf154.poster.avif?t=1737625652\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/217033f7c77149e8fe59a79c87fbf154.webm?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/217033f7c77149e8fe59a79c87fbf154.mp4?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乍一看，这个诗情画意的飘浮岛屿宛如人间仙境，但是一颗从天而降的小行星改变了一切。这一切到底是怎么回事？在出发踏上伟大征程之前，不要忘记收集避难所中的所有资源，然后……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将所有东西都砸个稀巴烂！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/041f54d7c7bde98168ae56fc0706026b.poster.avif?t=1737625652\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/041f54d7c7bde98168ae56fc0706026b.webm?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/041f54d7c7bde98168ae56fc0706026b.mp4?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >粉碎万物，不要放过沿途的任何东西，仔细收集制作材料、幼苗、资源以及能够丢向阻挡你进入魔镜的那些讨厌鼻涕虫的各类物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >方便快捷的嵌入制作系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/c5316a337ff7497b817bcd4ecdbe8bc9.poster.avif?t=1737625652\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/c5316a337ff7497b817bcd4ecdbe8bc9.webm?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/c5316a337ff7497b817bcd4ecdbe8bc9.mp4?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在眨眼之间组合包括表情在内的各类材料，随心所欲制作强力武器或美味零食，你不需要任何配方或者是制作站。品尝美食以获取加成，或者是将失败的料理丢向敌人以改变它们的属性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >捕捉可爱的生物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/9547e338bec38fa69694f947e62649af.poster.avif?t=1737625652\" width=596 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/9547e338bec38fa69694f947e62649af.webm?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/9547e338bec38fa69694f947e62649af.mp4?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你有没有幻想过拥有一个活力十足的棉花糖宠物？现在你终于可以梦想成真了！在手提箱中耕种并培育各种甜美生物，利用它们提供的资源来克服这场天马行空的冒险之旅途中的一切艰难险阻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在手提箱位面中建设技能建筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/a61f8327565a54c047909f5b4139e9ec.poster.avif?t=1737625652\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/a61f8327565a54c047909f5b4139e9ec.webm?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/a61f8327565a54c047909f5b4139e9ec.mp4?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用从外部世界中收集的资源，并在手提箱中*构筑*你的技能。气流旋翼机将允许你抵达难以企及的高处或者是轻松摆脱困境，有了手提箱旋涡之后，你将不用再与各种生物斗智斗勇，直接将它们吸进你的魔法手提箱吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战鼻涕大王并穿越魔镜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/6380524f7ee9b7361714545ba9036945.poster.avif?t=1737625652\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/6380524f7ee9b7361714545ba9036945.webm?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260200/extras/6380524f7ee9b7361714545ba9036945.mp4?t=1737625652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验趣味十足的战斗，食物就是你最大的武器！对抗宇宙鼻涕虫之王“鼻涕大王”，朝他投掷精心制作的美食并见证食物能够对敌人造成的惊人影响。无论是使用带有眩晕效果的甜食还是会让敌人发狂的辛辣料理，每一次的战斗都将是一场别开生面的*美食大战*！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
